  static const about_uz =
      "<![CDATA[ <p><strong>Wisdom</strong> lug'ati O'zbekistondagi eng ko\'p so\'z va iboralarni o\'z ichiga olgan va eng ishonarli manbalarga tayanib tuzilgan, mukammal va ishonchli lug\'at hisoblanadi. Bu lug\'at 5 yil davomida xalqaro ravishda tan olingan, yetakchi va ishonchli <em>Oxford, MacMillan, Collins, Cambridge </em>va<em> Longman</em> kabi Ingliz tili lug\'atlarida mavjud 80 000 dan ziyod so\'z va iboralarni o\'z ichiga olgan lug\'at bo\'lib, bu lug\'at o\'quvchilar uchun muhim bo\'lgan bir necha muhim xusiyat va jihatlarni o\'z ichiga oladi.</p> <p>Jumladan Wisdom lug\'ati tarkibida, ham Ingliz, ham O\'zbek tillaridagi so\'zlarning to\'liq va batafsil lug\'aviy ma\'nolari bilan birgalikda bu so\'zlarning qanday ishlatilishi va foydalanish qonun qoidalarini o\'z ichiga olgan <strong>Grammar</strong>, <strong>Collocations</strong> kabi bo\'limlarga ham ega. Shu bilan birga so\'zlar ishtirokidagi hayotiy gap va misollar o\'quvchiga kundalik hayotda so\'zlarning qanday ishlatilishi haqida to\'liq tushunchaga ega bo\'lishlariga ko\'maklashadi.</p> <p>Bundan tashqari so\'zning boshqa ma\'nodoshlari bilan tafovutlarini farqlab beruvchi <strong>Thesaurus</strong> va <strong>Difference</strong> bo\'limlari ham mavjud. So\'zga oid metafora va madaniyatlarini yoritib beruvchi, mos ravishda, <strong>Metaphor</strong> va <strong>Culture</strong> bo\'limlari ham foydalanuvchiga so\'z haqida qo\'shimcha va qimmatli ma\'lumotlarga ega bo\'lishlariga yordam beradi. Lug\'atning yana bir e\'tiborga loyiq jihatlari shundaki, so\'zning deyarli har bir ma\'nosiga mos sinonim (<strong>Synonyms</strong>) va antonimlar (<strong>Antonyms</strong>) berilgan. Bu o\'quvchining akademik insho va og\'zaki nutqlarida har xil lekin o\'xshash ma\'nolardagi so\'zlardan foydalanishiga yordam beradi.</p> <p>Bir so\'z bilan aytganda, <strong>Wisdom</strong> lug\'atini Ingliz-o\'zbek va o\'zbek-Ingliz ensiklopediyasi deyish mumkin, chunki bu lug\'atda har bir so\'zga ingliz tilidan to\'g\'ridan-to\'g\'ri alohida yondashilib qilingan tarjima, so\'zga aloqador grammatik qoidalar, foydalanish usullari, boshqa so\'zlar bilan farqi, sinonim va antonimlari, so\'z ishtirokidagi gaplar, so\'zning muqobil metaforasi va madaniyati, so\'z birikmalari, qanchalik faol tarzda ishlatilinish ko\'rsatkichi (yulduzcha bilan), akademik yoki ilmiy ekanligi, qaysi sohaga tegishliligi, qaysi predloglar bilan kelishi, qaysi sheva va laxjada ishlatilishi chuqur va keng tarzda yoritib o\'tilgan.</p><p>Ushbu lug\'at <strong>Wisdom</strong> o\'quv markazi asoschilari Abdullayev Xasanboy va Abdullayev Xusanboylar tomonidan tuzib chiqilgan bo\'lib, ular bundan tashqari bir necha boshqa Ingliz tiliga oid so\'zlashgich, lug\'at va boshqa kitob va mobil dasturlar mualliflari hisoblanishadi.</p> <p>Ular Toshkentdagi Singapurning Menejmentni Rivojlantirish Institutini 2012-yilda tamomlab <strong>Wisdom</strong> o\'quv markaziga asos solishgan va hozirda boshqa innovatsion darslik loyihalari ustida ish olib borishmoqdalar.</p>  <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>Texnik yordam, taklif va shikoyatlar uchun&nbsp; -&nbsp; support@wisdomedu.uz</p> <p>Barcha huquqlar himoyalangan &copy;2020 Wisdom Dictionary</p><p>Ilova &ldquo;Simpl Soution Team&rdquo; tomonidan ishlab chiqilgan</p>";
  static const about_en =
      "<![CDATA[ <p>Wisdom dictionary is considered to be the one in its kind, containing the most available words and it has been made up throughout five years, relying on the widely approved dictionaries such as <em>Oxford, MacMillan, Collins, Cambridge </em>and<em> Longman</em> dictionaries. It includes more than 80 000 words and phrases it owns several key features which will definitely be found useful by English learners.</p><p>Besides a rich and complete English and Uzbek word list, amazing features in the app like <strong>Grammar</strong> and <strong>Collocation</strong> allow users to gain valuable information regarding how to use the words in actual situations and explain grammar rules briefly and clearly. Furthermore, almost every word is followed by real examples making it easier and more efficient to remember and to use.</p><p>Moreover, Wisdom Dictionary has its own way of giving a clue about the difference and comparisons between close words, in terms of meaning, with the help of <strong>Thesaurus</strong> and <strong>Difference</strong> bar.</p><p>In order to have an extra understanding of the word, one needs to have idea about feedback and real meaning of the word. Additional features like <strong>Metaphor</strong> and <strong>Culture</strong> gives you this opportunity.</p><p>Another remarkable aspect of this app is that it includes <strong>Synonyms </strong>and<strong> Antonyms </strong>of nearly every word, more than any other dictionary apps available. Surely, it helps users to analyze and compare the words, being got remembered the other words simultaneously.</p><p>Shortly, <strong>Wisdom</strong> dictionary can be called an encyclopedia of English and Uzbek words and phrases as it is granted with all necessary features required by English learners.</p> <p>&nbsp;</p> <p>This dictionary was written and created by Abdullaev Khasanboy and Abdullayev Khusanboy who are claimed the creators of other English learning apps and books, and the founders of 